snippet: The San Francisco transit agency says it has reached a tentative agreement on a new contract with its union whose workers took part in a sickout that stalled the city's famed cable cars and disrupted other services....

headline.print_headline: San Francisco Transit Workers Reach Tentative Deal
headline.main: San Francisco Transit Workers Reach Tentative Deal

lead_paragraph: The San Francisco transit agency says it has reached a tentative agreement on a new contract with its union whose workers took part in a sickout that stalled the city's famed cable cars and disrupted other services.
